{"tid":601652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【預算案補漏】消息：低收入者可獲派4000元！　家庭主婦亦有份","createTime":"2018-03-22T11:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:37:51.000Z","uid":126594,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb813296aa9d60af3a71a3a351c9aa7a990001e","tid":601652,"uid":126594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波為預算案「拾遺補漏」，終極方案已敲定。據知情者透露，18歲以上、無收入或低收入人士、在今年預算案中未能受惠者，皆可獲派4000元，比最初傳聞的2000至3000元高一倍至三成三。由於符合以上三項條件的市民數量達百萬計，今次「派錢」範圍廣泛，一般家庭主婦、學生、退休人士都有機會受惠，舉例一個四口家庭，若夫婦二人及子女月入合乎低收入界線而又無領綜援等福利，便可合共取得16,000元現金津貼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/192545_c51d49f7504d3dc8a64140a84cc8616c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F192545_c51d49f7504d3dc8a64140a84cc8616c.jpg&h=809eb046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息指，政府將於日內公布預算案「拾遺補漏」方案，有關「低收入、無收入現金津貼」額高達4000元，比預算案建議向「有需要學生」一次過發放$2000津貼高出一倍。<br />\n<br />\n甚麼人可受惠呢？據了解，凡18歲以上、無收入或低收入而又在今年預算案中未能受惠於連串紓困措施，即綜援、生果金、長生津、傷殘津貼「出三糧」、寬免差餉等，即在涵蓋範圍之內。換言之，受惠者範圍相當廣，人數料以百萬計，所涉金額數十億元。<br />\n<br />\n知情者透露，今次「補漏」措施涵蓋面廣，連沒有工作的家庭主婦也可受惠，即使是中產家庭，「如果層樓冇佢個名，即係佢自己無享用到免差餉措施或其他派糖措施，咁就一樣收到4000元」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/170903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F170903&d=G4MbdYmg0nSFIzY5CecUOzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=37da14c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/170903</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底可唔可信？"},{"pid":"2c94622593b7620351547083fe4a12797bb1db2c","tid":601652,"uid":42072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"低收入係幾錢"},{"pid":"82b6d0cd013641e3740c060460ada81b4dfc3e4a","tid":601652,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:45:29.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有做野反而冇糖派"},{"pid":"827492ba5644013f0c75defb5efd4c7040889b46","tid":601652,"uid":162409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"如果層樓冇佢個名，即係佢自己無享用到免差餉措施或其他派糖措施，咁就一樣收到4000元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24550f10574e96856e9e88bbe3b849010f23b9a","tid":601652,"uid":125310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"依份budget，到下屆財政司上任，都未拾補遺漏完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f3ad92d3ac0484da0c68e609fad1b26148a095","tid":601652,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"一日多錢過一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d616fb59a6cb8bc8fd31220d1e2c73c0240228","tid":601652,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"吹多幾日，月尾正式公佈就會有10000啦"},{"pid":"cdb13a61e9a4a79c3747445c6ff5cd48b4ed1371","tid":601652,"uid":175004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"樓有名沒野做 就無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}